name: Lumbar Spinal Stenosis Protocol Video
descr:
The Lumbar Spinal Stenosis Practitioner Treatment protocol DVD video provides step-by-step instruction on how to applyall the specificmanual therapy techniques to your patient with lumbar spinal stenosis and how to implement the Boot Camp Program for Lumbar Spinal Stenosis in your clinical practice. Video duration 35 minutes.

 By Dr. Carlo Ammendolia.
